    <section id="RCF+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>RCF Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class="retired">The RCF project retired in 2009-09</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>The RCF project represents the incubation of a comprehensive
         library of JavaServer Faces components.  The intended destination of
         this project is the existing Apache MyFaces project.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="News">
      <title>News</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Project Terminated in Sept 2009, as it never got started.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    
